so I have to go out of service...

443
00:42:37.136 --> 00:42:41.936
but I'm not disturbed above.
I just believe what I believe.

444
00:42:42.077 --> 00:42:46.121
I'm just trying to understand.

445
00:42:46.221 --> 00:42:50.321
Did God tell you
not to pick up a gun?

446
00:42:50.454 --> 00:42:55.081
